{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t23-train-2","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"整式的加减","title":"针对训练2：整式加减综合","difficulty":4,"tags":["整式","加减"],"content":"已知 $A = 2x^2 - 3x + 1$，$B = x^2 + 2x - 3$，求 $2A - 3B$ 的值，当 $x = 2$ 时求其值。","steps":[{"title":"计算 2A - 3B","content":"$2A = 4x^2 - 6x + 2$\n\n$3B = 3x^2 + 6x - 9$\n\n$2A - 3B = 4x^2 - 6x + 2 - (3x^2 + 6x - 9)$\n\n$= 4x^2 - 6x + 2 - 3x^2 - 6x + 9$\n\n$= x^2 - 12x + 11$","formula":"x^2 - 12x + 11"},{"title":"代入求值","content":"当 $x = 2$：\n\n$= 4 - 24 + 11 = -9$","formula":"-9"}]},"id":"t23-train-2"},"__N_SSG":true}